{"id":2409,"date":"2024-02-03T09:31:50","date_gmt":"2024-02-03T02:31:50","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/?p=2409"},"modified":"2024-02-28T09:36:16","modified_gmt":"2024-02-28T02:36:16","slug":"xem-loto-mien-tay-ngam-chau-doc-lung-linh-ve-dem-tu-cap-treo-nui-sam-an-giang","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/xem-loto-mien-tay-ngam-chau-doc-lung-linh-ve-dem-tu-cap-treo-nui-sam-an-giang\/","title":{"rendered":"Xem l\u00f4 t\u00f4 mi\u1ec1n T\u00e2y, ng\u1eafm Ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ed1c lung linh v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00eam t\u1eeb c\u00e1p treo n\u00fai Sam An Giang"},"content":{"rendered":"\t\t<div data-elementor-type=\"wp-post\" data-elementor-id=\"2409\" class=\"elementor elementor-2409\" data-elementor-post-type=\"post\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-56d3d065 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"56d3d065\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-30e7fc46 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"30e7fc46\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<style>\/*! elementor - v3.18.0 - 20-12-2023 *\/\n.elementor-widget-text-editor.elementor-drop-cap-view-stacked .elementor-drop-cap{background-color:#69727d;color:#fff}.elementor-widget-text-editor.elementor-drop-cap-view-framed .elementor-drop-cap{color:#69727d;border:3px solid;background-color:transparent}.elementor-widget-text-editor:not(.elementor-drop-cap-view-default) .elementor-drop-cap{margin-top:8px}.elementor-widget-text-editor:not(.elementor-drop-cap-view-default) .elementor-drop-cap-letter{width:1em;height:1em}.elementor-widget-text-editor .elementor-drop-cap{float:left;text-align:center;line-height:1;font-size:50px}.elementor-widget-text-editor .elementor-drop-cap-letter{display:inline-block}<\/style>\t\t\t\t<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 detail-desc\">\n<div class=\"content-fck\">\n<div class=\"content-fck-font-size\">\n<div class=\"box-des-detail this-one\">\n<p class=\"knc-sapo\">Ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ebfn T\u1ebft, gi\u1edbi tr\u1ebb \u0111\u00e3 truy\u1ec1n tai nhau \u0111i\u1ec3m check in quen m\u00e0 l\u1ea1: th\u01b0\u1edfng l\u00e3m show l\u00f4 t\u00f4 mi\u1ec1n T\u00e2y t\u1eeb tr\u00ean cao, v\u1edbi h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh \u0111i c\u00e1p treo t\u1eeb ch\u00e2n l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh thi\u00eang n\u00fai Sam, tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh t\u00e2m linh vi\u1ebfng b\u00e0 ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 n\u00fai Sam.<\/p>\n<div class=\"knc-content\">\n<p><b>H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 n\u00fai Sam b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1p treo<\/b><\/p>\n<p>Khu du l\u1ecbch c\u00e1p treo N\u00fai Sam g\u1ed3m h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng c\u00e1p treo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 b\u1edfi c\u00f4ng ty MGA Vi\u1ec7t Nam, do c\u00e1c ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac s\u01b0 C\u1ed9ng h\u00f2a \u00c1o x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng. H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng c\u00e1p c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u d\u00e0i 900m v\u1edbi 37 cabin. M\u1ed7i cabin ch\u1edf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed1i \u0111a 8 kh\u00e1ch v\u00e0 di chuy\u1ec3n li\u00ean t\u1ee5c 24\/24 \u0111\u01b0a du kh\u00e1ch l\u00ean N\u00fai Sam vi\u1ebfng B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 chi\u00eam ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng nh\u1eefng c\u00f4ng tr\u00ecnh ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o kh\u00e1c.<\/p>\n<p>H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng c\u00e1p treo n\u00fai Sam n\u1eb1m trong qu\u1ea7n th\u1ec3 khu du l\u1ecbch c\u00e1p treo n\u00fai Sam t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9: Kh\u00f3m V\u0129nh T\u00e2y 3, ph\u01b0\u1eddng N\u00fai Sam, Th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ed1c, t\u1ec9nh An Giang. C\u00e1p treo N\u00fai Sam c\u00f3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1eafc \u0111\u1ecba, \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n Ch\u00f9a B\u00e0 v\u1edbi khu\u00f4n vi\u00ean 10 ha, b\u00e3i gi\u1eef xe c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c ch\u1ee9a h\u01a1n 2.000 \u00f4t\u00f4. V\u1edbi b\u1ed1n s\u1ea3nh nh\u00e0 h\u00e0ng v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng vi\u00ean r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i, tho\u00e1ng m\u00e1t&#8230;, n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c doanh nghi\u1ec7p ch\u1ecdn t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n, li\u00ean hoan, team building&#8230;<\/p>\n<div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\">\n<div><a class=\"detail-img-lightbox\" title=\"Khu du l\u1ecbch c\u00e1p treo v\u00e0 th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ed1c v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00eam nh\u00ecn t\u1eeb c\u00e1p treo\" href=\"https:\/\/channel.mediacdn.vn\/428462621602512896\/2024\/2\/3\/photo-1-1706935715581133860200.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-fancybox-group=\"img-lightbox\"><img decoding=\"async\" id=\"img_678100323213930496\" class=\"lightbox-content\" title=\"Xem l\u00f4 t\u00f4 mi\u1ec1n T\u00e2y, ng\u1eafm Ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ed1c lung linh v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00eam t\u1eeb c\u00e1p treo n\u00fai Sam An Giang - \u1ea2nh 1.\" src=\"https:\/\/channel.mediacdn.vn\/428462621602512896\/2024\/2\/3\/photo-1-1706935715581133860200.jpg\" alt=\"Xem l\u00f4 t\u00f4 mi\u1ec1n T\u00e2y, ng\u1eafm Ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ed1c lung linh v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00eam t\u1eeb c\u00e1p treo n\u00fai Sam An Giang - \u1ea2nh 1.\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-original=\"https:\/\/channel.mediacdn.vn\/428462621602512896\/2024\/2\/3\/photo-1-1706935715581133860200.jpg\" \/><\/a><\/div>\n<div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\">\n<p data-placeholder=\"[nh\u1eadp ch\u00fa th\u00edch]\">Khu du l\u1ecbch c\u00e1p treo v\u00e0 th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ed1c v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00eam nh\u00ecn t\u1eeb c\u00e1p treo<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p>T\u1eeb th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ed1c, An Giang, theo Qu\u1ed1c l\u1ed9 19 \u0111i th\u00eam 6km l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ebfn khu du l\u1ecbch. \u0110\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00fang c\u1ed5ng khu du l\u1ecbch, du kh\u00e1ch nh\u1edb ch\u1ea1y th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o b\u00e3i \u0111\u1eadu xe c\u00f3 b\u1ea3ng d\u1eebng ch\u1eef P, \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n ch\u1ebfch v\u1edbi c\u1ed5ng ch\u00f9a B\u00e0. Ngay ph\u00eda tay ph\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a c\u1ed5ng l\u00e0 qu\u1ea7y b\u00e1n v\u00e9 c\u00e1p treo. Nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean s\u1ebd h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111i\u1ec1u xe \u0111i\u1ec7n mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed, ch\u1edf du kh\u00e1ch t\u1eeb c\u1ed5ng v\u00e0o t\u1edbi nh\u00e0 ga l\u00ean c\u00e1p treo, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ch\u1edf kh\u00e1ch t\u1eeb nh\u00e0 ga \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e3i \u0111\u1eadu xe sau khi \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh chuy\u1ebfn th\u01b0\u1edfng ngo\u1ea1n t\u1eeb m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ea5t l\u00ean t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec9nh thi\u00eang c\u1ee7a n\u00fai Sam.<\/p>\n<p>T\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 ga d\u01b0\u1edbi ch\u00e2n n\u00fai &#8211; \u0111i\u1ec3m xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t c\u1ee7a h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh c\u00e1p treo, c\u00f3 nh\u00e0 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00e1ch d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i, k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi qu\u1ea7n th\u1ec3 ph\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh b\u1ed1n m\u00f9a, c\u1ea3nh s\u1eafc ba mi\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc\u2026 \u0111\u1ec3 du kh\u00e1ch th\u01b0\u1edfng ngo\u1ea1n, ch\u1ee5p h\u00ecnh k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m.<\/p>\n<p>Gi\u00e1 v\u00e9 tham kh\u1ea3o: 150k. Mua v\u00e9 ngay t\u1ea1i c\u1ed5ng v\u00e0o b\u00e3i \u0111\u1ed7 xe ho\u1eb7c qu\u1ea7y b\u00e1n v\u00e9 trong nh\u00e0 ga ch\u1edd.<\/p>\n<p><b>Nh\u1eefng tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khi kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 n\u00fai Sam b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1p treo<\/b><\/p>\n<p>\u0110i c\u00e1p treo, du kh\u00e1ch kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c c\u01b0\u1ee1i m\u00e2y, r\u1ebd gi\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh N\u00fai Sam, m\u00e0 c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u00eam ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng nh\u1eefng ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf m\u00f4 ph\u1ecfng nh\u1eefng ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Nh\u00e0 ga c\u00e1p treo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean h\u00ecnh m\u1eabu Nh\u00e0 th\u1edd \u0110\u1ee9c B\u00e0 t\u1ea1i Th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh. \u0110\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n c\u1eeda ch\u00ednh nh\u00e0 ga l\u00e0 qu\u1ea7n th\u1ec3 m\u00f4 ph\u1ecfng ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac ch\u00f9a m\u1ed9t C\u1ed9t v\u1edbi h\u1ed3 sen ph\u00eda d\u01b0\u1edbi n\u1edf quanh n\u0103m. Ph\u1ea7n kh\u00f4ng gian n\u1ed1i gi\u1eefa &#8220;ch\u00f9a m\u1ed9t C\u1ed9t&#8221; v\u00e0 c\u1eeda nh\u00e0 ga c\u00e1p treo, l\u00e0 h\u00e0ng tr\u0103m b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eafp \u0111\u1eb7t theo ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ec3 du kh\u00e1ch th\u01b0\u1edfng l\u00e3m v\u00e0 ch\u1ee5p h\u00ecnh: nh\u01b0 b\u00edch h\u1ecda, 36 ph\u1ed1 c\u1ed5 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, ru\u1ed9ng l\u00faa tr\u0129u h\u1ea1t, nh\u00e0 tre m\u00e1i l\u00e1 mi\u1ec1n T\u00e2y s\u00f4ng n\u01b0\u1edbc, m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec7m may mi\u1ec7t v\u01b0\u1eddn gi\u1ea3n d\u1ecb, \u0111\u01a1n s\u01a1&#8230; \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, t\u1eeb tr\u00ean cao du kh\u00e1ch c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed v\u0103n h\u00f3a mi\u1ec1n t\u00e2y qua nh\u1eefng show di\u1ec5n l\u00f4 t\u00f4 di\u1ec5n ra li\u00ean t\u1ee5c trong ng\u00e0y.<\/p>\n<div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode active\">\n<div><a class=\"detail-img-lightbox\" title=\"C\u00e1p treo \u0111\u01b0a du kh\u00e1ch l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh n\u00fai Sam vi\u1ebfng b\u1ec7 B\u00e0 ch\u00faa X\u1ee9, ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh t\u00e2m linh vi\u1ebfng B\u00e0\" href=\"https:\/\/channel.mediacdn.vn\/428462621602512896\/2024\/2\/3\/photo-1-1706935717267529755792.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-fancybox-group=\"img-lightbox\"><img decoding=\"async\" id=\"img_678100329773137920\" class=\"lightbox-content\" title=\"Xem l\u00f4 t\u00f4 mi\u1ec1n T\u00e2y, ng\u1eafm Ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ed1c lung linh v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00eam t\u1eeb c\u00e1p treo n\u00fai Sam An Giang - \u1ea2nh 2.\" src=\"https:\/\/channel.mediacdn.vn\/428462621602512896\/2024\/2\/3\/photo-1-1706935717267529755792.jpg\" alt=\"Xem l\u00f4 t\u00f4 mi\u1ec1n T\u00e2y, ng\u1eafm Ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ed1c lung linh v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00eam t\u1eeb c\u00e1p treo n\u00fai Sam An Giang - \u1ea2nh 2.\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-original=\"https:\/\/channel.mediacdn.vn\/428462621602512896\/2024\/2\/3\/photo-1-1706935717267529755792.jpg\" \/><\/a><\/div>\n<div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\">\n<p data-placeholder=\"[nh\u1eadp ch\u00fa th\u00edch]\">C\u00e1p treo \u0111\u01b0a du kh\u00e1ch l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh n\u00fai Sam vi\u1ebfng b\u1ec7 B\u00e0 ch\u00faa X\u1ee9, ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh t\u00e2m linh vi\u1ebfng B\u00e0<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p>Ng\u1ed3i c\u00e1p treo, du kh\u00e1ch c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 bao qu\u00e1t to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ed1c c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng bi\u00ean gi\u1edbi Vi\u1ec7t Nam &#8211; Cambodia. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u0111i c\u00e1p treo bu\u1ed5i t\u1ed1i, trong kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed h\u01a1i se l\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a mi\u1ec1n vi\u1ec5n bi\u00ean, to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ed1c v\u1edbi \u00e1nh \u0111\u00e8n lung linh v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00eam s\u1ebd \u0111em l\u1ea1i cho du kh\u00e1ch tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 ng\u1ed3i tr\u1ef1c th\u0103ng ng\u1eafm c\u1ea3nh.<\/p>\n<p>Sau khi \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea1m \u0111\u1ec9nh thi\u00eang n\u00fai Sam, l\u00e0m l\u1ec5 t\u1ea1i b\u1ec7 B\u00e0, tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh \u0111i b\u1ed9 xu\u1ed1ng nh\u00e0 ga c\u00e1p treo \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i xu\u1ed1ng, du kh\u00e1ch s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed thi\u00eang li\u00eang c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ec1n, ch\u00f9a, \u0111i\u1ec7n, \u0111\u00e0i v\u1edbi ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac c\u1ed5 x\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o. Quanh kh\u00f4ng gian n\u00e0y c\u00f2n c\u00f3 h\u1ed3 c\u00e1 Koi, thung l\u0169ng t\u00ecnh y\u00eau\u2026 d\u00e0nh cho c\u00e1c c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i, nh\u1eefng b\u1ea1n tr\u1ebb v\u1edbi mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea7u t\u00ecnh duy\u00ean linh \u1ee9ng\u2026.<\/p>\n<p>Ngo\u00e0i Mi\u1ebfu B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa x\u1ee9 N\u00fai Sam, S\u01a1n l\u0103ng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u, ch\u00f9a T\u00e2y An, ch\u00f9a Hang, du kh\u00e1ch c\u00f2n c\u00f3 d\u1ecbp chi\u00eam b\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi anh em song sinh v\u1edbi t\u01b0\u1ee3ng &#8220;Ph\u1eadt ng\u1ecdc h\u00f2a b\u00ecnh th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi&#8221; n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng.<\/p>\n<div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\">\n<div><a class=\"detail-img-lightbox\" title=\"T\u01b0\u1ee3ng Ph\u1eadt ng\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00fac t\u1eeb kh\u1ed1i ng\u1ecdc b\u00edch n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng v\u00f9ng \u0110\u00f4ng B\u1eafc Vancouver (Canada)\" href=\"https:\/\/channel.mediacdn.vn\/428462621602512896\/2024\/2\/3\/photo-2-1706935717881659939993.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-fancybox-group=\"img-lightbox\"><img decoding=\"async\" id=\"img_678100332104704000\" class=\"lightbox-content\" title=\"Xem l\u00f4 t\u00f4 mi\u1ec1n T\u00e2y, ng\u1eafm Ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ed1c lung linh v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00eam t\u1eeb c\u00e1p treo n\u00fai Sam An Giang - \u1ea2nh 3.\" src=\"https:\/\/channel.mediacdn.vn\/428462621602512896\/2024\/2\/3\/photo-2-1706935717881659939993.jpg\" alt=\"Xem l\u00f4 t\u00f4 mi\u1ec1n T\u00e2y, ng\u1eafm Ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ed1c lung linh v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00eam t\u1eeb c\u00e1p treo n\u00fai Sam An Giang - \u1ea2nh 3.\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-original=\"https:\/\/channel.mediacdn.vn\/428462621602512896\/2024\/2\/3\/photo-2-1706935717881659939993.jpg\" \/><\/a><\/div>\n<div class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\">\n<p data-placeholder=\"[nh\u1eadp ch\u00fa th\u00edch]\">T\u01b0\u1ee3ng Ph\u1eadt ng\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00fac t\u1eeb kh\u1ed1i ng\u1ecdc b\u00edch n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng v\u00f9ng \u0110\u00f4ng B\u1eafc Vancouver (Canada)<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p>Kh\u1ed1i ng\u1ecdc d\u00f9ng ch\u1ebf t\u00e1c t\u01b0\u1ee3ng Ph\u1eadt ng\u1ecdc N\u00fai Sam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khai th\u00e1c t\u1ea1i v\u00f9ng \u0110\u00f4ng B\u1eafc Vancouver (Canada), n\u01a1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ec7nh danh l\u00e0 khu m\u1ecf ng\u1ecdc b\u00edch c\u1ee7a th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Ban \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u1ed1i ng\u1ecdc c\u00f3 tr\u1ecdng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng kho\u1ea3ng 10 t\u1ea5n. Sau khi s\u1edf h\u1eefu kh\u1ed1i ng\u1ecdc b\u00edch, C\u00f4ng ty C\u1ed5 ph\u1ea7n MGA Vi\u1ec7t Nam, v\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n sang Th\u00e1i Lan v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ee3 \u0111i\u00eau kh\u1eafc h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb v\u00f9ng Chiang Rai th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n.<\/p>\n<p>\u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t t\u1ea1i, \u0110\u1ec1n Ph\u1eadt Ng\u1ecdc &#8211; n\u01a1i c\u00f3 t\u01b0\u1ee3ng Ph\u1eadt Th\u00edch Ca M\u00e2u Ni \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ebdo g\u1ecdt t\u1ec9 m\u1ec9 t\u1eeb kh\u1ed1i ng\u1ecdc th\u00f4 c\u00f3 tr\u1ecdng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 10 t\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ebfn B\u1ec7 B\u00e0, t\u1ecda l\u1ea1c ngay t\u1ea1i th\u00e1p Ph\u00e1o \u0110\u00e0i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00f3. C\u00f3 l\u1eddi t\u01b0\u01a1ng truy\u1ec1n r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 n\u01a1i B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 N\u00fai Sam t\u1eebng ng\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00edn c\u00f4 g\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed3ng trinh th\u1ec9nh xu\u1ed1ng ch\u00e2n n\u00fai, nay g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 Mi\u1ebfu B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 N\u00fai Sam Ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ed1c.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ebfn T\u1ebft, gi\u1edbi tr\u1ebb \u0111\u00e3 truy\u1ec1n tai nhau \u0111i\u1ec3m check in quen m\u00e0 l\u1ea1: th\u01b0\u1edfng l\u00e3m show l\u00f4 t\u00f4 mi\u1ec1n T\u00e2y t\u1eeb tr\u00ean cao, v\u1edbi h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh \u0111i c\u00e1p treo t\u1eeb ch\u00e2n l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh thi\u00eang n\u00fai Sam, tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh t\u00e2m linh vi\u1ebfng b\u00e0 ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 n\u00fai Sam. H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn kh\u00e1m [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":2414,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[79],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2409"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2409"}],"version-history":[{"count":4,"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2409\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":2413,"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2409\/revisions\/2413"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/2414"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=2409"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=2409"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=2409"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}